item.title: CVE-2023-42805|2024-08-02T19:30:24.143Z -- quinn-rs -- quinn
item.description: quinn-proto is a state machine for the QUIC transport protocol. Prior to versions 0.9.5 and 0.10.5, receiving unknown QUIC frames in a QUIC packet could result in a panic. The problem has been fixed in 0.9.5 and 0.10.5 maintenance releases.
